snippet: Cam Levins was the star of the Armory Track Invitational in Manhattan, pulling off a stunning double win in the one-mile and two-mile races and beating the Olympic silver medalist Galen Rupp in completing the feat.
abstract: Cam Levins wins one-mile and two-mile races at Armory Track Invitational in Manhattan.
lead_paragraph: Cam Levins was the star of the Armory Track Invitational in Manhattan, pulling off a stunning double win in the one-mile and two-mile races and beating the Olympic silver medalist Galen Rupp in completing the feat.

headline.main: Canadian Upsets Olympic Medalist in Winning 2 Races
headline.print_headline: Canadian Upsets Olympic Medalist in Winning 2 Races
